    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0

    v0 = (wp.cos(wp.sin(v2 + 0.64)) + v0)
    v2 = (wp.exp(wp.exp(v1 + 0.31)) - 0.51)
    v0 = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.79) / wp.sin(v0 + 0.60)) / 0.06)
    v1 = (0.31 * wp.exp((v2 + 0.32 - tmp + 0.47)))
    data[tid] = v0
